title: Total population of Russia 2024
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Inhabitants in millions. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Inhabitants in millions has decreased over the Year.
Inhabitants in millions is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2016, roughly constant from 2016 to 2019, and finally slightly decreasing from 2019 to 2024.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
Maximum Inhabitants in millions, about 146.9 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Inhabitants in millions about 145.74 was reached at Year 2024
